{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Gale Avatar has gotten Elminster's message that he should kill the Absolute... and himself in the process."
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "0": {
      "id": "0",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*Elminster's visit weighs heavy on your mind. His is a face you did not expect to see again.*",
      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale lies on his bedroll, restless",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "6",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "10": {
          "id": "10",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*When you last saw him, you were in your prime. No orb. No tadpole. A mage of growing renown, all power, pride and potential - beloved by the goddess of magic herself.*",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "6",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "20": {
              "id": "20",
              "speaker": "Narrator",
              "text": "*It's one thing to have fallen from such heights, but to have Elminster himself now witness your humilation is almost unbearable.*",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "6",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "9": {
                  "id": "9",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "His disappointment cuts deeper even than Mystra's. He was your hero...",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "6",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "4": {
                      "id": "4",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*While most know of Elminster the legend, few know him as you have. He plucked you from obscurity. Offered you his guidance. His faith. And most recently, his pity.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "6",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                },
                "12": {
                  "id": "12",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "You wonder, did he even try to intervene on your behalf?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "6",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "2": {
                      "id": "2",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Elminster has served Mystra loyally for centuries. If he has any doubts, he's keeping them close to his chest.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "6": {
                          "id": "6",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*The stakes of the task ahead are clear. The Absolute threatens more than Faer\u00fbn. It threatens the goddess of magic herself.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "3": {
                              "id": "3",
                              "speaker": "Gale",
                              "text": "You think on the Netherese magic affecting your tadpole. A magic Mystra abhors...",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "14": {
                                  "id": "14",
                                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                                  "text": "*The last great threat to Mystra's role as protector of the Weave was at the hands of the Netherese wizard, Karsus.*",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "21": {
                                      "id": "21",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*His empire, Netheril, has long since crashed and burned, but traces of its magic still remain, if you know what to look for. Spells. Artefacts. Weapons...*",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "1": {
                                          "id": "1",
                                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                                          "text": "*Whatever lies at the Heart of the Absolute, it's powerful enough to inspire the fear of the gods themselves. What else could it be capable of?*",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "19": {
                              "id": "19",
                              "speaker": "Gale",
                              "text": "To wield enough power to threaten a god. That would be quite something...",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "24": {
                                  "id": "24",
                                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                                  "text": "*Somewhere in these shadow-cursed lands lies a power great enough that Mystra dare not speak its true name.*",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "5": {
                                      "id": "5",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*'The Heart of the Absolute'... You will find it where it beats, and learn exactly what she's afraid of.*",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "26": {
                              "id": "26",
                              "speaker": "Gale",
                              "text": "The Absolute must be stopped. If this is the only way, so be it.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "22": {
                                  "id": "22",
                                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                                  "text": "*You've witnessed first-hand the Absolute's depravity. It's quite something to know you now have the power to wipe it from existence with a snap of your fingers.*",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "16": {
                                      "id": "16",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*You'd die too, of course, but your name would live on. 'Gale of Waterdeep, the Light of Faer\u00fbn.' If only you might live to see it.*",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "15": {
                              "id": "15",
                              "speaker": "Gale",
                              "text": "You failed her once. You will not fail her again.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "7": {
                                  "id": "7",
                                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                                  "text": "*Destroy the Heart of the Absolute, and you may yet turn your greatest mistake into your greatest triumph.*",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "18": {
                                      "id": "18",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*Something stirs within you. Hope. There may yet be a chance of redemption for Gale of Waterdeep after all.*",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "17": {
                  "id": "17",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "He would never inflict such cruel terms on you. Mystra must have forced his hand.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "6",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "11": {
                      "id": "11",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Mystra would no more forgive Elminster for defying her than she was willing to forgive you. His hands are tied. As, it seems, are yours.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "6",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                },
                "25": {
                  "id": "25",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "Doddering old fool. Trust him to leave the hard work to you.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "13": {
                      "id": "13",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Elminster's a relic concerned only with preserving his own legend. He couldn't care less if this mission would rob you of your own legacy.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "8": {
                          "id": "8",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*Or, perhaps it's Mystra who fears she will be erased. The Heart of the Absolute not only threatens mortal life. It threatens her too.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "23": {
                              "id": "23",
                              "speaker": "",
                              "text": "",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "6",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "jump",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}